{
  "chapter": "094",
  "title": "田儋列传",
  "translations": {
    "1": {
      "title": "田儋起事",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田儋</span>是<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">狄</span>人，是故<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>王<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">田氏</span>的族人。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：田儋\">儋（田儋）</span>的从弟<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田荣</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：田荣\">荣（田荣）</span>之弟<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田横</span>，都豪强，宗族强大，能得人心。"
    },
    "2": {
      "title": "自立为齐王",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陈涉</span>刚起事称王<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>地时，派<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">周市</span>略定<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>地，北至<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">狄</span>，<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">狄</span>城防守。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田儋</span>假装绑缚自己的奴，带领少年到县廷，想拜见县令说要<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span>奴。一见<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">狄令</span>，就<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">击</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span>县令，召集<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">豪吏</span>子弟说：\"<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>都反<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">自立</span>，〖◆齐</span>是古之建国，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：田儋\">儋（田儋）</span>是<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">田氏</span>，应当称王。\" 便<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">自立</span>为<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>王，发兵<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">击</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">周市</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">周市</span>军撤走，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田儋</span>便率兵东略定<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>地。"
    },
    "3": {
      "title": "田儋战死",
      "text": "<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>将<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">章邯</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">围</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>王<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：魏咎\">咎（魏咎）</span>于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">临济</span>，情势紧急。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>王向<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>求救，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>王<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田儋</span>率兵救<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">章邯</span>夜里衔枚偷<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">击</span>，大<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">破</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>军，在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">临济</span>之下<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田儋</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：田儋\">儋（田儋）</span>之弟<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田荣</span>收<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：田儋\">儋（田儋）</span>余兵东走<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">东阿</span>。"
    },
    "4": {
      "title": "立田假为王",
      "text": "<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>人听说王<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田儋</span>死，便立故<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>王<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：田建\">建（田建）</span>之弟<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田假</span>为<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>王，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田角</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">相</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田间</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">将</span>，以抵抗<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>。"
    },
    "5": {
      "title": "田荣立田市",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田荣</span>逃到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">东阿</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">章邯</span>追<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">围</span>他。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">项梁</span>听说<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田荣</span>情势紧急，便率兵在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">东阿</span>之下<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">击</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">破</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">章邯</span>军。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">章邯</span>西走，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">项梁</span>便追击。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田荣</span>怒<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">立</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：田假\">假（田假）</span>，便率兵归<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">击</span>逐<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>王<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：田假\">假（田假）</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：田假\">假（田假）</span>逃到<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">相</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：田角\">角（田角）</span>逃到<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>；<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：田角\">角（田角）</span>之弟<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田间</span>先前求救于<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>，便留下不敢归。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田荣</span>便<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">立</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田儋</span>之子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：田市\">市（田市）</span>为<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>王。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：田荣\">荣（田荣）</span>相之，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田横</span>为将，平<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>地。"
    },
    "6": {
      "title": "齐拒救楚赵",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">项梁</span>追击<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">章邯</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">章邯</span>兵势益盛，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">项梁</span>派使者告<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>，请他们发兵共击<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">章邯</span>。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田荣</span>说：\"让<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田假</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田角</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田间</span>，才肯出兵。\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">楚怀王</span>说：\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田假</span>是盟国之王，穷困归投我，<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span>之不义。\" <span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>也不<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田角</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田间</span>与<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>交易。 <span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>说：\"<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">蝮</span>蛇螫手就<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">斩</span>手，螫足就<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">斩</span>足。为什么？因为有害于身。如今<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田假</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田角</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田间</span>对于<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>，非但不是手足之亲，又为何不<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span>？再说<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>若再得志于天下，则我等当事者都要被掘坟了。\" <span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>不听，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>也怒，终不肯出兵。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">章邯</span>果然<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">败</span>并<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">项梁</span>，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">破</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>兵，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>兵东走，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">章邯</span>渡河<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">围</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">钜鹿</span>。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">项羽</span>前去救<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>，因此怨<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田荣</span>。"
    },
    "7": {
      "title": "分封三齐",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">项羽</span>已救<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>，降<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">章邯</span>等人，西屠<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">咸阳</span>，灭<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>而<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">立</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">侯王</span>，便迁<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>王<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田市</span>改王<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">胶东</span>，治所<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">即墨</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>将<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田都</span>跟从共救<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>，因而入关，故<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">立</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：田都\">都（田都）</span>为<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>王，治<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">临淄</span>。故<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>王<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：田建\">建（田建）</span>之孙<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田安</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">项羽</span>正渡河救<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>时，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田安</span>下<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">济北</span><span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">数城</span>，率兵降<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">项羽</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">项羽</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">立</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田安</span>为<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">济北</span>王，治<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">博阳</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田荣</span>因负<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">项梁</span>不肯出兵助<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>，所以不得王；<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>将<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陈馀</span>也失职不得王：<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">二人</span>都怨<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：项羽\">项王（项羽）</span>。"
    },
    "8": {
      "title": "田荣并三齐",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：项羽\">项王（项羽）</span>既归国，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>各归本国，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田荣</span>派人率兵助<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陈馀</span>，令他反<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>地，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：田荣\">荣（田荣）</span>也发兵抵御<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">击</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田都</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田都</span>逃至<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田荣</span>扣留<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>王<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：田市\">市（田市）</span>，不让他去<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">胶东</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：田市\">市（田市）</span>的左右说：\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：项羽\">项王（项羽）</span>强暴，而王应到<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">胶东</span>，不就国，必危险。\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：田市\">市（田市）</span>恐，便偷偷去就国。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田荣</span>怒，追<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">击</span>在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">即墨</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>王<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：田市\">市（田市）</span>，回来再<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">济北</span>王<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：田安\">安（田安）</span>。于是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田荣</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">自立</span>为<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>王，尽并三<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>之地。"
    },
    "9": {
      "title": "田荣败死",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：项羽\">项王（项羽）</span>听说，大怒，便北<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">伐</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>王<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田荣</span>兵<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">败</span>，走<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">平原</span>，<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">平原</span>人<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：田荣\">荣（田荣）</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：项羽\">项王（项羽）</span>便烧夷<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>城郭，所过之处尽屠之。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>人相聚叛之。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：田荣\">荣（田荣）</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">弟</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：田横\">横（田横）</span>收<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>散兵，得<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">数万人</span>，在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">城阳</span>反<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">击</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">项羽</span>。而<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>王率<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">败</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>，入<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">彭城</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">项羽</span>闻之，便撤<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>而归，在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">彭城</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">击</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>，便连着与<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">战</span>，相持于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">荥阳</span>。所以<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田横</span>得以再收<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>城邑，<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">立</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田荣</span>之<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：田广\">广（田广）</span>为<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>王，而<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：田横\">横（田横）</span>相之，专国政，政事无论大小都由<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">相</span>决断。"
    },
    "10": {
      "title": "韩信平齐",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：田横\">横（田横）</span>定<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">三年</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>王派<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：郦食其\">郦生（郦食其）</span>前去游说<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>王<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：田广\">广（田广）</span>及其<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">相国</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：田横\">横（田横）</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：田横\">横（田横）</span>同意，解除<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">历下</span>的军备。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>将<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">韩信</span>率兵正要东<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">击</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>起初派<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">华无伤</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田解</span>驻军于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">历下</span>以抗<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>使者到后，便罢守<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">战</span>备，纵酒，还派使者与<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>讲和。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>将<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">韩信</span>已平<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>，用<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">蒯通</span>计，渡<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">平原</span>，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">袭</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">破</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">历下</span>军，便入<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">临淄</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>王<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：田广\">广（田广）</span>、<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">相</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：田横\">横（田横）</span>大怒，以为<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：郦食其\">郦生（郦食其）</span>出卖自己，便烹<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：郦食其\">郦生（郦食其）</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>王<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：田广\">广（田广）</span>东走<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">高密</span>，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">相</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：田横\">横（田横）</span>走<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">博</span>，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">守相</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田光</span>走<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">城阳</span>，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">将军</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田既</span>驻军于<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">胶东</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>派<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">龙且</span>救<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>王与他合军于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">高密</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>将<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">韩信</span>与<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">曹参</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">破</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">龙且</span>，虏<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>王<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：田广\">广（田广）</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>将<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">灌婴</span>追得<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">守相</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田光</span>。到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">博</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：田横\">横（田横）</span>听说<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>王死，<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">自立</span>为<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>王，还<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">击</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：灌婴\">婴（灌婴）</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：灌婴\">婴（灌婴）</span>在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">嬴下</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">败</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：田横\">横（田横）</span>之军。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田横</span>亡走<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">梁</span>，归<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">彭越</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">彭越</span>当时居<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">梁</span>地，中立，或为<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>，或为<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">韩信</span>已<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">龙且</span>，便令<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">曹参</span>进兵在<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">胶东</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">破</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田既</span>，派<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">灌婴</span>在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">千乘</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">破</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>将<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田吸</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">韩信</span>于是平<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>，请求<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">自立</span>为<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">假王</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>就立他为王。"
    },
    "11": {
      "title": "田横入海",
      "text": "后来<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">一年多（时长）</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>灭<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">项籍</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>王<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">立</span>为<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">皇帝</span>，以<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">彭越</span>为<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">梁</span>王。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田横</span>惧被<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">诛</span>，与他的徒属<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">五百馀人</span>入海，居岛中。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高帝</span>闻之，以为<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田横</span>兄弟本定<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>人贤者多附他们，如今在海中不收服，日后恐为乱，便派使者<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">赦</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田横</span>之罪召他来。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田横</span>辞谢说：\"<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>烹<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">陛下</span>之使者<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：郦食其\">郦生（郦食其）</span>，如今听说他的弟弟<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">郦商</span>为<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>将且贤能，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>恐惧，不敢奉诏，请为庶人，守在海岛中。\" 使者回报，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高皇帝</span>便诏<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">卫尉</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">郦商</span>说：\"<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>王<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田横</span>即将来到，人马随从敢动摇者灭<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">族</span>！\" 又派使者持节详告诏<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：郦商\">商（郦商）</span>之事，说：\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田横</span>来，大则可王，小则为侯；不来，即举兵加<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">诛</span>。\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田横</span>便与他的两个客人乘传车至<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">洛阳</span>。"
    },
    "12": {
      "title": "田横自刎",
      "text": "距<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">洛阳</span>未到<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">三十里</span>，到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">尸乡</span>驿站，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：田横\">横（田横）</span>辞谢使者说：\"做臣子见<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">天子</span>当洗沐。\" 便停留下来。对他的客人说：\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：田横\">横（田横）</span>当初与<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>王同样南面称孤，如今<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>王为<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">天子</span>，而<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：田横\">横（田横）</span>却为亡虏而北面事之，这耻辱已经够大了。况且我煮了人家的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">兄</span>，与其<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">弟</span>并肩事奉同一个主上，纵然他畏<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">天子</span>之诏，不敢动我，我自己心里不愧吗？况且<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">陛下</span>想见我，不过是想见一面我的面貌而已。如今<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">陛下</span>在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">洛阳</span>，现在<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">斩</span>我头，驰<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">三十里</span>路程，容貌还不会<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">败</span>坏，尚可辨认。\" 便自刎，令客人捧其头，随使者驰奏于<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高帝</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高帝</span>说：\"唉，有道理啊！从布衣起家，兄弟<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">三人</span>相继为王，岂非贤能！\" 为他流涕，并拜他的两位客人为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">都尉</span>，发卒<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">二千人</span>，以王者礼葬<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田横</span>。"
    },
    "13": {
      "title": "五百壮士",
      "text": "葬毕，两位客人在坟旁挖洞，都自刎，下从<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田横</span>于地下。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高帝</span>闻之，大惊，称赞<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田横</span>的客人都贤能。我听说还有<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">五百人</span>在海中，派使者召他们。使者到则听说<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田横</span>已死，他们也都<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">自杀</span>。于是才知道<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田横</span>兄弟真能得<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士</span>之心。"
    },
    "14": {
      "title": "太史公曰",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">太史公</span>说：太厉害了<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">蒯通</span>之谋，搅乱<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>使<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩信\">淮阴（韩信）</span>骄纵，最终使这<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">两人</span>亡身！<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">蒯通</span>善于纵横之说，评论<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">战国</span>时期的权变，著有八十一篇。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：蒯通\">通（蒯通）</span>善待<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>人<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">安期生</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">安期生</span>曾干谒<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">项羽</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">项羽</span>不能用其策。后来<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">项羽</span>想封此<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">两人</span>，<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">两人</span>终不肯受，逃走了。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田横</span>之高节，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">宾客</span>慕义而随<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：田横\">横（田横）</span>而死，岂非至贤！我因此记载他们。不是没有善画者，但无人能为之画像，为什么呢？"
    },
    "15": {
      "title": "赞",
      "text": "<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span><span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">项</span>之际，天下交兵。 <span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">六国</span>树党，各自安置豪英。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田儋</span>殒于寇难，<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">立</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：田市\">市（田市）</span>，相辅<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：田荣\">荣（田荣）</span>。 <span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>封王<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：田假\">假（田假）</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">破</span>烹<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：郦食其\">郦生（郦食其）</span>。 <span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">兄弟</span>相继为王，海岛传声名。"
    }
  }
}